description: Prickster is where blockchain brilliance meets pure mischief! We're the first indexed collection of 10,000 unique characters spun from over 600 traits and our first of a kind bridge lets you bounce between Bitcoin and Fractal like a true Trickster. We’ve woven these digital pranksters together with clever recursive magic, making each one a masterpiece of on-chain trickery. Whether you’re in it for the art or the antics, we got the goods. Dive into the rarity, cross the bridge, and join the prank!
name: Prickster
